      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 15 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 15 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>謙，亨，君子有終。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Qian indicates progress and success. The superior man, (being humble as it implies), will have a (good) issue (to his undertakings).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
