      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 15 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 15 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：謙謙君子，用涉大川，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows us the superior man who adds humility to humility. (Even) the great stream may be crossed with this, and there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
