      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：鳴謙，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows us humility that has made itself recognised. With firm correctness there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
