      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：勞謙君子，有終吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows the superior man of (acknowledged) merit. He will maintain his success to the end, and have good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
