      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 15 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：不富，以其鄰，利用侵伐，无不利。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows one who, without being rich, is able to employ his neighbours. He may advantageously use the force of arms. All his movements will be advantageous.</seg>
