      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 15 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六：鳴謙，利用行師，征邑國。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The sixth SIX, divided, shows us humility that has made itself recognised. The subject of it will with advantage put his hosts in motion; but (he will only) punish his own towns and state.</seg>
      </tuv>
